===Etymology===
Simplified in the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]] from the [[man'yōgana]] kanji [[毛]] ([[もう]], [[mō]]), meaning hair.

===Hiragana character===
{{ja-kana|rom=mo}}

# The [mo] syllable.
# The thirty-fifth character in the [[gojūon]] ordering of [[hiragana]]. The previous character is [[め]] and the next character is [[や]]. The equivalent [[katakana]] character is [[モ]].

